description:
This is a 13 minute workout called '10 Minute HIIT Express Elliptical Workout | MAX EFFORT PYRAMID' from the channel Sunny Health & Fitness.
The workout falls under Cardio/Elliptical and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: If you're thinking 10 minutes isn't enough time to squeeze in a workout, then this 10 Min All Out Pyramid HIIT Elliptical Workout will definitely change your mind! Hop on your elliptical or cardio climber and follow along with Sunny Trainer Brittany as she guides you through constantly changing intervals designed to push your body to the max burning big calories along the way!
